%% Diagram: Attachment upload — presigned multipart upload with antivirus scan
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as Issue API
    participant S3I as S3 incoming bucket
    participant SCAN as Scanner (Lambda + ClamAV / GuardDuty)
    participant S3C as S3 clean bucket
    participant S3Q as S3 quarantine bucket
    participant DB as Postgres

    C->>API: POST /attachments {filename, size, mime}
    API->>API: validate quota, mime, size cap
    API-->>C: presigned multipart URL + objectKey
    C->>S3I: PUT parts (direct upload, multipart)
    S3I-->>C: ETag per part
    C->>API: complete upload
    API->>S3I: CompleteMultipartUpload
    S3I-->>SCAN: S3:ObjectCreated event
    SCAN->>SCAN: scan(objectKey)
    alt clean
        SCAN->>S3C: copy + delete from incoming
        SCAN->>API: notify(clean, objectKey)
        API->>DB: insert attachments(issue_id, key, size)
    else infected
        SCAN->>S3Q: copy + delete from incoming
        SCAN->>API: notify(infected, objectKey)
    end
